{
    "version": 5,
    "bundle": "S35R4L53TO2IHC4Z742ZMFJ6IDKBS3AA",
    "type": "story",
    "storyId": "041010005",
    "title": "レイニーデイの奇跡",
    "text": [
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "空から降り注ぐ大粒の雨が、激しく窓を叩いている。\r\n朝の天気予報いわく、午後には止むとの話だが……。",
            "enText": "Large rain drops were incessantly falling, striking the window. \nAccording to the morning weather forecast, it was supposed to \nclear up in the afternoon, though…",
            "nextBlock": 2,
            "origClipLength": 135,
            "pathId": -6018439178759288317,
            "blockIdx": 1
        },
        {
            "jpName": "タイキシャトル",
            "enName": "Taiki Shuttle",
            "jpText": "たのも～～～～！！",
            "enText": "Pardon me~~~~!!!",
            "nextBlock": 3,
            "origClipLength": 64,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 50,
                    "pathId": -2610454755440352302
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 36,
                    "pathId": -6405096550567552947
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8010918165771727406,
            "blockIdx": 2
        },
        {
            "jpName": "タイキシャトル",
            "enName": "Taiki Shuttle",
            "jpText": "トレーナーさん、ハウディ～！\r\n今日はトレーニングの日なのに、雨ザーザーです！",
            "enText": "Trainer-san, Howdy~! \nToday's a training day but, the rain is really coming down!",
            "nextBlock": 4,
            "origClipLength": 227,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 138,
                    "pathId": 8200526657924556572
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 77,
                    "pathId": 1576455878099079180
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3682554631258617569,
            "blockIdx": 3
        },
        {
            "jpName": "タイキシャトル",
            "enName": "Taiki Shuttle",
            "jpText": "なので……お願いがありマス！",
            "enText": "So… I have a request!",
            "nextBlock": 5,
            "origClipLength": 130,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": -5173603667158119665
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 5565814275703555607
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 6120680251297108752,
            "blockIdx": 4
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "まさかこの土砂降りの雨の中、走りたいとでも言うのだろうか。\r\nいくらなんでも風邪をひいて――",
            "enText": "Don't tell me that, in the middle of this downpour, she wants to \nrun. She'd probably catch a cold-",
            "nextBlock": 6,
            "origClipLength": 105,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 133,
                    "pathId": 5517741412144041603
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6941460871502261359,
            "blockIdx": 5
        },
        {
            "jpName": "タイキシャトル",
            "enName": "Taiki Shuttle",
            "jpText": "一緒にテルテル坊主を作りまショウ！！",
            "enText": "Let's make a teru teru bozu!!",
            "nextBlock": 7,
            "origClipLength": 98,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "え、てるてる坊主？",
                    "enText": "Eh, a teru teru bozu?",
                    "nextBlock": 7
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 45,
                    "pathId": -3777733633188373881
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 36,
                    "pathId": 7691456037824869138
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 223448730829658403,
            "blockIdx": 6
        },
        {
            "jpName": "タイキシャトル",
            "enName": "Taiki Shuttle",
            "jpText": "実は、さっきクラスのみんなが話してたんデス。\r\n『外で思いっきり走りたいのに』って。",
            "enText": "Just now, everyone in class was talking about it. \nSaying [I really wanted to run outside, though].",
            "nextBlock": 8,
            "origClipLength": 250,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 86,
                    "pathId": -7256510732751770240
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8518739330197874995,
            "blockIdx": 7
        },
        {
            "jpName": "タイキシャトル",
            "enName": "Taiki Shuttle",
            "jpText": "とってもとってもションボリ。\r\n教室の中まで、どんよりデース。",
            "enText": "They were really really downhearted. \nEven the classroom seems kind of gloomy.",
            "nextBlock": 9,
            "origClipLength": 175,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": 4070933218104058551
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 74,
                    "pathId": -5095051068507142796
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 650866690336181229,
            "blockIdx": 8
        },
        {
            "jpName": "タイキシャトル",
            "enName": "Taiki Shuttle",
            "jpText": "そこでワタシ、ひらめきマシタ。テルテル坊主を作ろうと！\r\nしかもスーパービッグなテルテル坊主デス！！",
            "enText": "So then, I had an idea. I wanna make a Teru teru bozu! \nNot just any one, but a super big teru teru bozu!!",
            "nextBlock": 10,
            "origClipLength": 324,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 80,
                    "pathId": -6594592828371037686
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 21,
                    "pathId": 5373373594679019741
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -6121635150432648735,
            "blockIdx": 9
        },
        {
            "jpName": "タイキシャトル",
            "enName": "Taiki Shuttle",
            "jpText": "スーパービッグなら、きっとパワーもビッグ！\r\nハリケーンだって、あっという間に晴れちゃいマス！",
            "enText": "If it's super big, then it's power will be just as big! \nEven a hurricane would clear up in an instant!",
            "nextBlock": 11,
            "origClipLength": 240,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": -3163395697209100775
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 21,
                    "pathId": 7108725972335103825
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 36,
                    "pathId": 3644161586100337701
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 1369304351619297561,
            "blockIdx": 10
        },
        {
            "jpName": "タイキシャトル",
            "enName": "Taiki Shuttle",
            "jpText": "というわけで、トレーナーさん！\r\nそこのカーテンをくだサーイ！",
            "enText": "So that's why, Trainer-san! \nPlease let me have that curtain!",
            "nextBlock": 12,
            "origClipLength": 161,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "カーテンで作るのか！？",
                    "enText": "Making it out of a curtain?!",
                    "nextBlock": 12
                },
                {
                    "jpText": "カーテンで作るの！？",
                    "enText": "Making it out of a curtain?!",
                    "nextBlock": 12
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 64,
                    "pathId": -6926348101677955522
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 58,
                    "pathId": -2618112220814462869
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -3185675955036001328,
            "blockIdx": 11
        },
        {
            "jpName": "タイキシャトル",
            "enName": "Taiki Shuttle",
            "jpText": "ザッツライ！　任せてくだサイ！\r\nパワフルなテルテル坊主で、必ず晴れさせてみせマース！",
            "enText": "That's right! Leave it to me! \nWith a powerful teru teru bozu, it'll definitely clear up!",
            "nextBlock": 13,
            "origClipLength": 261,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 155,
                    "pathId": 520309433408795635
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 30,
                    "pathId": -3172382533910412791
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1643088803070916937,
            "blockIdx": 12
        },
        {
            "jpName": "タイキシャトル",
            "enName": "Taiki Shuttle",
            "jpText": "これでみんなもハッピー・スマイルですネ。\r\nさぁ、始めまショウ！",
            "enText": "And with that, everyone will show me their happy smiles. \nAlright, let's get started!",
            "nextBlock": 14,
            "origClipLength": 187,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": 2018639161271734252
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 36,
                    "pathId": 4683287360987375993
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8255800321396161589,
            "blockIdx": 13
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "友だちを思うタイキシャトルの気持ちを無下には出来ない。\r\nしかし、このままでは備品のカーテンがてるてる坊主に……！",
            "enText": "It's hard to refuse Taiki Shuttle's feelings when she's \nthinking about her friends. But, at this rate the \ncurtains will become a teru teru bozu…!",
            "nextBlock": 15,
            "origClipLength": 119,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "も、もっとビッグな布で作ろう！",
                    "enText": "L-let's use a bigger cloth!",
                    "nextBlock": 15
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": 8074481073693433207
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -7150121063110910321,
            "blockIdx": 14
        },
        {
            "jpName": "タイキシャトル",
            "enName": "Taiki Shuttle",
            "jpText": "ホワ……ホワッツ！？　もっと、ビッグな……！？",
            "enText": "Wha… what?! A bigger one…?!",
            "nextBlock": 16,
            "origClipLength": 154,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 45,
                    "pathId": -4260000841385617457
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -5265691281790418856,
            "blockIdx": 15
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "保健室でいらなくなったベッドシーツをもらい、\r\n縫い合わせて大きな一枚の布を作った。",
            "enText": "I went to the infirmary and grabbed a few unused bedsheets. \nI sewed them together into one larger piece.",
            "nextBlock": 17,
            "origClipLength": 99,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 112,
                    "pathId": 4848452158870056560
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2646305807959418782,
            "blockIdx": 16
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "そして――",
            "enText": "And then-",
            "nextBlock": 18,
            "origClipLength": 51,
            "pathId": -3082999222627835801,
            "blockIdx": 17
        },
        {
            "jpName": "タイキシャトル",
            "enName": "Taiki Shuttle",
            "jpText": "さぁ、あとは窓に飾るだけデス。\r\nトレーナーさん、チアー・アップ！",
            "enText": "Alright, now we just need to hang it by the window. \nTrainer-san, cheer up!",
            "nextBlock": 19,
            "origClipLength": 213,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "お、重い……！",
                    "enText": "H-heavy…!",
                    "nextBlock": 19
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -8516537332175865222,
            "blockIdx": 18
        },
        {
            "jpName": "タイキシャトル",
            "enName": "Taiki Shuttle",
            "jpText": "ふぅ～。ビッグなテルテル坊主は、\r\n窓にかけるのもボーンが折れマス。",
            "enText": "Fuuu~. Hanging a big teru teru bozu \nby the window is bone breaking work.",
            "nextBlock": 20,
            "origClipLength": 217,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 182,
                    "pathId": -4526590699520151462
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 45,
                    "pathId": 6465725643121800560
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8819319859548046891,
            "blockIdx": 19
        },
        {
            "jpName": "タイキシャトル",
            "enName": "Taiki Shuttle",
            "jpText": "でもたいそー立派な坊主ができマシタ！\r\nポイントはこのキュートなスマイルですヨ♪",
            "enText": "But, it's a wonderful big bozu! \nAnd the main point is this cute smile it has!",
            "nextBlock": 21,
            "origClipLength": 254,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": -6872375008616881695
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 100,
                    "pathId": -3433733550470909448
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 4213713021154470432,
            "blockIdx": 20
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "人間サイズのてるてる坊主が、窓に吊るされている。\r\n……お化け屋敷の一室のようだ。",
            "enText": "A human-sized teru teru bozu was hanging by the window. \n…it was more like a room in a haunted house.",
            "nextBlock": 22,
            "origClipLength": 98,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": -7291782294569509910
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": -5429091965084430355
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 2414613517765962845,
            "blockIdx": 21
        },
        {
            "jpName": "タイキシャトル",
            "enName": "Taiki Shuttle",
            "jpText": "イヤッホォーーー！！　オーケー！\r\nこれで雨雲を吹き飛ばし――……オウ！？",
            "enText": "Yahooooo!! Okay! \nNow all those rain clouds will-…Oh?!",
            "nextBlock": 23,
            "origClipLength": 231,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": 4204063092829402127
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 119,
                    "pathId": 4274118424970297671
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 36,
                    "pathId": -3923315844201658078
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -4279330693481102474,
            "blockIdx": 22
        },
        {
            "jpName": "タイキシャトル",
            "enName": "Taiki Shuttle",
            "jpText": "トレーナーさん、太陽デス！！",
            "enText": "Trainer-san, it's the sun!!",
            "nextBlock": 24,
            "origClipLength": 100,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": 5692454961112727576
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 77,
                    "pathId": 6028443043545211743
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8410971768010013949,
            "blockIdx": 23
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "窓から空を見上げると、いつの間にか雨は止み\r\n雲の切れ間から太陽が顔を出していた。",
            "enText": "When I looked outside the window at the sky, at some point the \nrain had stopped and the sun was out between a gap in the clouds.",
            "nextBlock": 25,
            "origClipLength": 98,
            "pathId": 9017926474456345752,
            "blockIdx": 24
        },
        {
            "jpName": "タイキシャトル",
            "enName": "Taiki Shuttle",
            "jpText": "アメージング！　さすがニホンのマジックアイテム！\r\nアーンド、トレーナーさんとワタシのパワー！",
            "enText": "Amazing! Leave it to a real life magic item! \nAnd, Trainer-san and my power!",
            "nextBlock": 26,
            "origClipLength": 290,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": -3150247734445218721
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 38,
                    "pathId": -8656787197820454200
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3455003264851406164,
            "blockIdx": 25
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "タイキシャトルは嬉しそうに外を眺めている。\r\n……天気予報のことは、このまま伝えずにおこう。",
            "enText": "Taiki Shuttle was excitedly gazing outside. \n…I won't tell her about the weather report.",
            "nextBlock": 27,
            "origClipLength": 105,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 96,
                    "pathId": 736290397940506211
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 117,
                    "pathId": 5704539750882648151
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 8225416936000815205,
            "blockIdx": 26
        },
        {
            "jpName": "タイキシャトル",
            "enName": "Taiki Shuttle",
            "jpText": "すっかりトレーニング日和！\r\nこれならフルパワーで走れそうデスネ！",
            "enText": "It's completely become a beautiful day for training! \nIf it's like this, I can run using my full power!",
            "nextBlock": 28,
            "origClipLength": 185,
            "choices": [
                {
                    "jpText": "それじゃさっそく――",
                    "enText": "Then, let's get to it-",
                    "nextBlock": 28
                }
            ],
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 60,
                    "pathId": -7264134013318787969
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 20,
                    "pathId": 5590565758902866157
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1242977969045499219,
            "blockIdx": 27
        },
        {
            "jpName": "タイキシャトル",
            "enName": "Taiki Shuttle",
            "jpText": "イエーースッ！　みんなのスマイル見てきマース！",
            "enText": "Yeeees! I'm gonna go see everyone's smiles!",
            "nextBlock": 29,
            "origClipLength": 138,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 39,
                    "pathId": -755517241768598938
                },
                {
                    "origLen": 36,
                    "pathId": -1740793272239391677
                }
            ],
            "pathId": -1858687739529571803,
            "blockIdx": 28
        },
        {
            "jpName": "",
            "enName": "",
            "jpText": "呼びかける声も届かず、タイキシャトルは元気いっぱいに\r\n走り去ったのだった……。",
            "enText": "With a loud voice that could reach out, \na lively Taiki Shuttle ran off…",
            "nextBlock": -1,
            "origClipLength": 97,
            "animData": [
                {
                    "origLen": 82,
                    "pathId": 2887967857229808703
                }
            ],
            "pathId": 3204808323982857607,
            "blockIdx": 29
        }
    ],
